$nanoDesc1='The Nano Unicorn project is a unique initiative under the ‘Skilled-in-Odisha’ banner that handpicks entrepreneurial talent in the state. It aims to encourage skilled youth to take up entrepreneurship by linking them to philanthropic capital. The resultant small indigenous enterprises not only strengthen the economy but also generate employment at the grass roots.';

$nanoDesc2='The Nano Unicorns begin their journey with a capital of Rs 1 lakh. In venture capital parlance when the valuation of the start-up exceeds $ 1 billion, the Nano Unicorn becomes a Unicorn. Examples of such start-ups are Flipkart, Ola etc.';

$nanoDesc3='We provide short entrepreneurship training of 80 hours over 10 days to the Nano Unicorns. This power packed crash course makes them confident to plunge into the challenging path of transforming themselves from being Job seekers to Job creators.';

$nanoDesc4='After attending the training, the Nano Unicorns are supported with initial capital to commence their business with regular periodic mentoring from experts.';

$nanoDescnew='The seed capital is made available to OSDA through philanthropic donors. We have supported  100 such entrepreneurs during 2017-18, and intend to support 1000 in the year 2018-19 and 3000 in the year 2019-20.';

$nanoDesc5='How to Become a Nano Unicorn';
 
$nanoDesc6='Pre-requisite';

$nanoDesc7='The person must be trained and certified in a vocation by an ITI or a Polytechnic or should have completed a short term skill training program recognized by government and must have a business idea. The concerned institution must recommend the prospective  Nano Unicorn considering the dedication, need and strength of business idea of the candidate.';

$nanoDesc8='Selection';

$nanoDesc9='The prospective Nano Unicorns have to undergo a two-step selection process. The first step is to accomplish a given series of activities called the “Activity Centre” including playing a “Knack” game on the mobile phone. Successful candidates will then be interviewed by a panel.';

$nanoDesc10='Training';

$nanoDesc11='Selected candidates  undergo  a rigorous, residential training programme of 10 days on Entrepreneurship Development and prepare their business plan during the training. They also get to understand loan disbursement and repayment protocols, mentorship schedule and undergo assessment. At the end of training they get a certificate of participation.';

$nanoDesc12='Funding';

$nanoDesc13='All certified participants, upon signing an agreement with OSDA are eligible for receiving funding upto Rs 1 lakh. No guarantee or collateral will be required. For the first year the entrepreneur will not be charged any interest on the Rs. 1 lakh. During the second year a nominal 5% interest will be charged. From the third year the outstanding will be payable at 12% interest.';

$nanoDesc14='Business Kick-Off';

$nanoDesc15='Post training the amount is transferred to the prospective entrepreneur’s bank account directly. They utilize the funds to kick-start their planned business.';

$nanoDesc16='Aim of Nano Unicorn';

$nanoDesc17='The aim of Nano Unicorn project is to assist this transformation and help nourish and nurture the dreams of  those youth who have no access to collaterals and capital but have the fire in their belly to become an entrepreneur. ';
	
$nanoDesc18='Knowledge Hub';

$nanoDesc19='This is a repository of information by the Nano Unicorns for the Nano Unicorns. Additionally, it has the inspiring journeys of all the Nano Unicorns.';

$nanoDesc20='The experience so far';

$nanoDesc21='The project was initiated by OSDA in July 2017 and till now (as of end of July 2020) 12 batches have completed their training and support has been extended to 250 entrepreneurs out of which 51 are women.243 of them have given financial assistance of 2.31 Cr in total. Almost all of them have come from economically disadvantaged families and have shown tremendous amount of grit and determination. Most of them are ready to mentor the upcoming new entrepreneurs and make their family proud.';

$nanoDesc22='Mentoring & Monitoring';
$nanoDesc23='Each Nano Unicorn is mentored by Subject Matter Experts and / or business experts and nurtured for at least 15 hours over a year with quarterly reviews for course-corrections, if needed. During the initial phase,the frequency of mentoring is higher.This  business site of each and every entrepreneur is visited by OSDA team. All entrepreneurs are encouraged to network with the other Nano Unicorn. As the business stabilises and expands, the shy unsure youngsters evolve into confident entrepreneurs';





$process='How to Become a Nano Unicorn';
$meet='Meet the Nano Unicorns';
$register='Register for Nano Unicorn';

$nanounicorn='Nano Unicorn';









